quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  10,43,"ino e ma…ď…ďe on ndaaroowo ma. e ko aan fewnata bum…óo oon, hay si wonii …ďe nji'atah?"
  10,44,"Pellet Alla too√Īirta yim…ďe …ďeen huunde, ko woni, ko yim…ďe …ďe too√Īata ko'e muen."
  10,45,"√Ďande o moo…ďoyta …ďe, wa'ata kona si …ďe √Īii…ďaano si wanaa sa'a gooto e √Īalawma, he…ďe nganndandira hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. GooŇč…óii …ďeen yeddu…ďe kawral Alla ngal sooyii, …ďe ngonaano feew…ďe."
  10,46,"Si min kollii ma yoga e ko ko min podani…ďe, maa …óuum min ∆īettitii ma, (fow e mun), ko faade ka amen woni ruttorde ma…ď…ďe. refti Alla ko ceedii…óo e ko …ďe ngollata ko."
  10,47,"Hino woodani mofte kala nulaa…óo. Si nulaa…óo ma…ď…ďe on arii, √Īaawiree hakkunde ma…ď…ďe nuun…óal, kam…ďe …ďe too√Īetaake."
  10,48,"He…ďe mbi'a: "Ko honnde tuma woni ndee fodoore, si on laatike gooŇčgu…ďe?""
  10,49,"Maaku : "mi waawanaa hoore am lorra wanaa nafa si wanaa ko Alla muuyi. Hino woodani mofte kala lajal. Si lajal ma…ď…ďe ngal arii, …ďe nee…ďnirantaake saa'a …ďe ngardinantaake kadi"."
  10,50,"Maaku : "kaalaneekam, si lepte makko …óe ngarii e mon jemma maa √Īalawma, ko hol…óum bon…ďe …ďe hawjiranta …óe?""
  10,51,"E ko tuma …óe yani ngooŇč…óin ton …óe? e ko jooni noon, gooŇč…óii on laatinoke he√Īanii…ďe …óum?"
  10,52,"Refti too√Ī…ďe …ďen mbi'anee : "mee…óee lepte luttugol. hara on njo…ďete si wanaa kon ngonno…óon e faggitaade?""
  10,53,"He…ďe kabrino maa : "…óuum ko goonga?" maaku : "Ko non, mi woo…óndirii joomi am, pellet ko …óe goonga. on ngonaani roŇčkinoo…ďe"."